{"tid":421490,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係我有問題定佢有問題","createTime":"2017-10-02T09:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T09:59:17.000Z","uid":26852,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"40ff0547774bc4240f5a72b29f847eac8a202ae0","tid":421490,"uid":26852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:39:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n最近換左新電話 <br />\n咁我啲舊相都有幾千張 所以就全部一早backup晒落電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁新機就冇晒相 其實我就會有種用新機就重新再黎過嘅感覺 好爽<br />\n當然啦 我覺得係個人喜好黎 你自己鍾意點處理啲相就點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問題就黎啦 琴日比我條女發現我電話啲相冇晒<br />\n就開始發癲 話咩幾年回憶冇晒 逼我入返晒入電話<br />\n又話冇人用新機會唔backup舊機相入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實當時我立即解釋左自己諗法 話我地咪可以再影新嘅 同埋舊相我一早就backup晒電腦啦 最後更加有保留少部分比較近期嘅合照落新機<br />\n<br />\n佢而家仲係咁話得返咁少相 係到發脾氣 <br />\n究竟係咪真係我好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e862a649be788a1fde6feeea968e59d0c1472175","tid":421490,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d44cd24409508d0a87c947642b0c0c6f08dc8a2","tid":421490,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"佢有問題 <br />\n你有backup已經好好 但我個個冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5eb4debb1bd0a873321e83c12de0d6279e2fcec","tid":421490,"uid":15658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"咪成日遲到啦"},{"pid":"ba119ec7f77bab34de6bd25c0393837574da45ce","tid":421490,"uid":26852,"like":0,"dislike":0,